  "date": "2026-01-29 13:00:00",
  "author": "笔记侠",
  "siteName": "笔记侠",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <div data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100006036\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 325px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2e8dfd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib82e0KnQ48deDEHe6kUgFNh6NIbdWmyCibZHvJEuqxT4Q6mxic1B0ficwkk3rb3ZOicbN5iaMwxiaAXGF1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源</span></span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| &nbsp;</span><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align: right;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;font-family:微软雅黑;widows:1;\"><span leaf=\"\">中信出版社&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;出版</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 书籍《</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;text-decoration: rgb(70, 70, 70);\"><span leaf=\"\">贪婪的多巴胺</span></span><span leaf=\"\">》【美】</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:right;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:rgb(70, 70, 70);\"><span leaf=\"\">迈克尔·E.朗</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 著</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编</span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| 柒 &nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">排版</span></strong><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;| 沐言</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: #0000007a;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 16px;widows: 1;text-align: right;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">第 9417</span></strong></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">篇深度好文：3516</span></strong></strong></strong></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">字 | 11 分钟阅读</span></strong></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">人生有两大悲剧，一是夙愿未果，一是得偿所愿</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span><span><span leaf=\"\">—— 萧伯纳《凡人与超人》</span></span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">人脑中最重要的化学物质就是多巴胺</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">它是理解我们感受到的冲动以及我们为什么会做出如此反应的关键</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">处理浪漫关系、区分欲望与关心、抵制社交媒体诱惑、摆脱购物上瘾…… 几乎所有与选择和动力相关的场景，都离不开多巴胺的身影。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">多巴胺驱动我们去获得和发现，这是它的进化目的，为了让我们活下去｡但在安全富足的现代社会，这种曾经的生存优势，却常常让我们陷入欲求不满的循环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们建造了能满足大部分需求的世界，却依然被多巴胺驱使着追逐 “更多”，在社交媒体的无限刷新中消耗时间，在无意义的购物冲动中浪费资源，在短暂的目标达成后迅速陷入空虚</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种对 “更多” 的执念，既是进步的引擎，也可能成为成长的枷锁。唯有驯服多巴胺，在欲望与成长之间找到平衡，才能突破困局，收获真正的满足与意义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;text-align:center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100006013\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59d10dee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9HlfMVIF2fuDvkLpxdtWG5Cxf1mITOyPu6JEYp4A0mfCia1Xiaba5UjDkBtLjmVuBHBCoUCQggiabGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">《贪婪的多巴胺2》重磅上市，教你如何掌控多巴胺，而不是让多巴胺控制你，升情绪力、专注力和创造力。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin: 10px 0em;outline: 0px;\">\n    <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;width: 556.364px;background: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, #a0a0a0, #fff7ea00) #ae515100;\">\n     <div mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;padding: 5px 10px;outline: 0px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一、</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid #b00c03;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid #b00c03;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration:none solid rgb(176, 12, 3);font-size:17px;\"><span leaf=\"\">认知觉醒：</span></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-decoration: none solid rgb(176, 12, 3);\"><span leaf=\"\">多巴胺的双重面孔与成长陷阱</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.多巴胺的本质：欲望的引擎与失控的风险</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">多巴胺系统由欲望多巴胺和控制多巴胺两个子系统组成</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;\"><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">欲望多巴胺系统促使人们追求可能具有存在价值的新鲜事物，它基于诱惑而非事实；控制多巴胺系统则为我们提供想象、计划和执行的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;text-align:center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100006035\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=001dccdc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9HlfMVIF2fuDvkLpxdtWG5ayXbOjGbXufqIz6icWLwCK6CWTHEXLLiahfLKQicmC5MUIDAIKTAcupsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">对早期人类来说，这种对潜在风险和回报始终保持敏感的做法至关重要，但在现代世界，过度的欲望多巴胺会让我们陷入无意义的追逐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们渴望某样东西，追逐它，最终拥有它，却往往只获得短暂的快乐，推动我们前进的力量同样会把我们推向绝望。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">就像经典美剧《办公室》中雷恩・威尔森，名利双收却依然痛苦，总觉得自己应该收获更多，这正是典型的多巴胺体验。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论拥有多少，它总会引导我们越过此时此刻向前看，暗示未拥有的才是幸福的关键。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;text-align:center;\" data-imgfileid=\"100006034\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9fe27607&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9HlfMVIF2fuDvkLpxdtWG5P81EeVcyqQGBfExKI2ToLjdQNN56kepfS1yB0zA7YGtI4rQO0YwwGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">更值得警惕的是，我们越频繁地刺激多巴胺系统中的任何特定通路，就越需要更多的刺激才能产生反应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">过度沉迷于社交媒体的点赞、游戏的升级、购物的即时满足，会让快乐阈值不断升高，最终陷入 “快乐减弱、渴望不减” 的成瘾困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.成长的核心：打破 “追逐 - 失望” 的循环</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">驯服多巴胺，首先要学会在 “当下快乐” 与 “未来价值” 之间做出明智权衡。让我们能长久生存的东西，很少能让我们现在快乐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:0px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100006019\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=571cc967&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2hkT8Z52Rib9HlfMVIF2fuDvkLpxdtWG5P81EeVcyqQGBfExKI2ToLjdQNN56kepfS1yB0zA7YGtI4rQO0YwwGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">去上班能付房租却想睡懒觉，吃健康餐有益身体却想吃垃圾食品，存薪水以备不时之需却想买新玩具，这种在当下快乐和明天的 “如果” 之间的权衡，是人类经验的核心特征。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">不快乐是人脑固有的，但它也是最大的动力之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">快乐的人不会改进自己，也不会改善世界，这种不适感会激励我们创造更好的东西。我们需要接受这种不适感，将其转化为成长的动力，而不是被欲望多巴胺驱使着逃避。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的成长，始于认清多巴胺的本质，它的承诺未必可靠，不加节制的追逐只会让我们在欲望的跑步机上疲于奔命。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mp-plugin=\"96weixin\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC